# Mesh automation is ENABLED while this file exists in the repo root.
#
# The .github/workflows/mesh-cron.yml workflow checks for this file
# before running. To disable the cron without editing the workflow,
# delete this file and push. To re-enable, re-add it.
#
# This is a deliberate kill switch — a file is harder to leave on by
# accident than a GitHub Actions variable.
